---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | Elegant Lashes by Katie"
  description="Terms of Service for Elegant Lashes by Katie. Review our terms and conditions for using our lash extension services in Orange County."
>
  <Navigation />

  <main class="pt-20 min-h-screen bg-gradient-ghibli py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="ghibli-card p-8 md:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-darktext mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-mediumtext mb-8">Effective Date: January 1, 2025</p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-darktext">
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              By accessing our website at elegantlashesbykatie.com or using our lash extension services at any of our Orange County locations (Irvine, Tustin, Santa Ana, Costa Mesa), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use our website or services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">2. Services Description</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Elegant Lashes by Katie provides professional lash extension services including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Classic lash extensions</li>
              <li>Volume lash extensions</li>
              <li>Hybrid lash extensions</li>
              <li>Lash fills and maintenance</li>
              <li>Lash removal services</li>
              <li>Lash consultations</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any service at any time without notice.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">3. Appointment Booking and Cancellation</h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Booking</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Appointments can be made through our website, by phone at 657-334-9919, or in person at any of our locations. All appointments are subject to availability.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Cancellation Policy</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Cancellations must be made at least 24 hours in advance</li>
              <li>Late cancellations (less than 24 hours) may result in a cancellation fee</li>
              <li>No-shows will be charged 50% of the scheduled service cost</li>
              <li>Repeated no-shows may result in requirement of advance payment for future bookings</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Late Arrivals</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Clients arriving more than 15 minutes late may need to reschedule their appointment. If we can accommodate late arrivals, service time may be shortened to avoid delays for subsequent clients.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">4. Payment Terms</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Payment is due at the time of service</li>
              <li>We accept cash, credit cards, and debit cards</li>
              <li>Prices are subject to change without notice</li>
              <li>Promotional offers are subject to specific terms and conditions</li>
              <li>Gift certificates are non-refundable and must be used within one year of purchase</li>
              <li>Refunds are issued at our discretion on a case-by-case basis</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">5. Client Health and Safety</h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Disclosure Requirements</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Clients must disclose the following information before receiving services:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Allergies to adhesives, cosmetics, or other products</li>
              <li>Eye conditions or infections</li>
              <li>Recent eye surgeries or procedures</li>
              <li>Pregnancy or nursing status</li>
              <li>Use of contact lenses</li>
              <li>Any medical conditions that may affect lash application</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Contraindications</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We reserve the right to refuse service if we determine that lash extensions are not appropriate for your health or safety.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Allergic Reactions</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              While rare, allergic reactions to lash adhesive or products can occur. If you experience redness, swelling, itching, or discomfort, contact us immediately and seek medical attention if necessary.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">6. Aftercare and Maintenance</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Clients are responsible for following aftercare instructions provided by our lash artists. Failure to properly care for lash extensions may result in:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Premature lash loss</li>
              <li>Damage to natural lashes</li>
              <li>Eye irritation or infection</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We are not responsible for damage caused by improper aftercare, self-removal attempts, or use of incompatible products.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">7. Liability and Warranties</h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Elegant Lashes by Katie, its owners, employees, and affiliates shall not be liable for any damages arising from:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Allergic reactions to products used during service</li>
              <li>Damage to natural lashes from improper aftercare</li>
              <li>Individual variations in lash retention</li>
              <li>Pre-existing eye conditions or sensitivities</li>
              <li>Indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">No Warranties</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee specific results or lash retention periods, as individual results vary.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              All content on our website, including text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of Elegant Lashes by Katie and protected by copyright and trademark laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">9. Photography and Social Media</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We may photograph your lash work for promotional purposes. By receiving our services, you consent to the use of your photos on our website, social media, and marketing materials unless you explicitly opt out in writing.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              If you wish to opt out of photography, please inform your lash artist before your appointment.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">10. Age Requirements</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Clients must be at least 18 years of age to receive lash extension services. Clients under 18 must be accompanied by a parent or legal guardian who must provide written consent.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">11. Professional Conduct</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We expect all clients to treat our staff with respect. We reserve the right to refuse service or terminate appointments if clients engage in:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Abusive, threatening, or inappropriate behavior</li>
              <li>Harassment of any kind</li>
              <li>Intoxication or substance impairment</li>
              <li>Violation of our studio policies</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">12. Website Use</h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-3">Prohibited Activities</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Use our website for any unlawful purpose</li>
              <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
              <li>Transmit viruses, malware, or harmful code</li>
              <li>Interfere with the proper functioning of our website</li>
              <li>Scrape, harvest, or collect user information</li>
              <li>Impersonate any person or entity</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">13. Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of service of these external sites.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">14. Indemnification</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Elegant Lashes by Katie from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, and expenses arising from your violation of these Terms of Service or your use of our services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">15. Governing Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              These Terms of Service are governed by the laws of the State of California. Any disputes arising from these terms or our services shall be resolved through binding arbitration in Orange County, California, in accordance with the rules of the American Arbitration Association.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">16. Severability</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              If any provision of these Terms of Service is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">17. Changes to Terms</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to our website. Your continued use of our services after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-darktext mb-4">18. Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
            <div class="bg-accent/30 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold mb-2">Elegant Lashes by Katie</p>
              <p class="mb-1">Email: <a href="mailto:elegantlashesbykatie@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary">elegantlashesbykatie@gmail.com</a></p>
              <p class="mb-1">Phone: <a href="tel:+16573349919" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary">657-334-9919</a></p>
              <p class="mb-1">Location: 15333 Culver Dr #220, Irvine, CA 92604</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <p class="text-sm text-mediumtext italic">
              By using our services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and our Privacy Policy.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose a {
    @apply text-primary hover:text-secondary transition-colors underline;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    @apply border-b border-primary/20 pb-2;
  }

  .prose p {
    @apply text-darktext leading-relaxed;
  }
</style>
